[Cite as 06/26/2003 Case Announcements #2, 2003-0hio-3321.]

CASE ANNOUNCEMENTS AND ADMINISTRATIVE ACTIONS

June 26, 2003

MOTION AND PROCEDURAL RULINGS

1991-2137. State v. Campbell.

Hamilton App. No. C-890330. Upon consideration of appellant’s motion for stay of execution pending review by this court of Supreme Court case No. 2003-1101,

IT IS ORDERED by the court that the motion for stay be, and hereby is, denied.

Moyer, C.J., Resnick, F.E. Sweeney, Pfeifer, Lundberg Stratton, O’Connor and O’Donnell, JJ., concur.
